        "id": 1114919
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-08-12T01:12:55Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "^ ideally, fieldmask would be specified here, based on which the QueryOption would be specified in RPC to Gerrit.",
      "revId": "bc513f5931752b196617bcb26c25ee4c1ebeee00",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
      "unresolved": false
