      "message": "I\u0027m absolutely fine to go with existing QueryOption.\n\n(2) 100% agree.\n(1) not sure I follow. User should specify what they actually need:\n  label.*      \u003d\u003e ADVANCED_LABELS + DETAILED_ACCOUNTS.\n  label.*.name \u003d\u003e would be just \"LABELS\" option.\n\nAnyways, let\u0027s proceed as is.",
